#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:4
msgid "Retriever to use:"
msgstr "Y cyrchydd i'w ddefnyddio:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:4
msgid ""
"The retriever is responsible for fetching installer components to be loaded."
msgstr "Mae'r cyrchydd yn gyfrifol am gyrchu cydrannau sefydlydd i'w llwytho."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../templates:11
msgid "Installer components to load:"
msgstr "Cydrannau sefydlydd i'w llwytho:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../templates:11
msgid ""
"Most things you will need will be loaded automatically. The listed installer "
"components all have low priority and are probably not necessary, but may be "
"interesting to some users."
msgstr ""
"Caiff y rhan fwyaf o bethau byddwch angen eu llwytho'n awtomatig. Mae gan y "
"cydrannau sefydlydd a rhestrir flaenoriaeth isel a mwy na thebyg dydyn nhw "
"ddim yn angenrheidiol, ond fe allent fod o ddiddordeb i rhai defnyddwyr."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../templates:11
msgid ""
"Note that if you select a component that requires others, those components "
"will also be loaded."
msgstr ""
"Sylwch os rydych chi'n dewis cydran sy'n dibynnu ar eraill, caiff y "
"cydrannau hynny eu llwytho hefyd."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. (Progress bar) title displayed when loading udebs
#: ../templates:22
msgid "Loading components of the Debian installer"
msgstr "Yn llwytho cydrannau sefydlydd Debian"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:26
msgid "Retrieving ${PACKAGE}"
msgstr "Yn cyrchu ${PACKAGE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:30
msgid "Unpacking ${PACKAGE}"
msgstr "Yn dadbacio ${PACKAGE}"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:34
msgid "Failed to load installer component"
msgstr "Methwyd llwytho cydran sefydlydd"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:34
msgid "Loading ${PACKAGE} failed for unknown reasons. Aborting."
msgstr "Methwyd llwytho ${PACKAGE} am resymau anhysbys. Yn erthylu."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Main menu item
#: ../load-installer.templates:4
msgid "Load installer components"
msgstr "Llwytho cydrannau sefydlydd"

#~ msgid "Failed to retrieve installer component"
#~ msgstr "Methwyd cyrchu cydran sefydlydd"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Retrieving the component ${PACKAGE} failed for unknown reasons. Aborting."
#~ msgstr "Methwyd cyrchu'r cydran ${PACKAGE} am resymau anhysbys. Yn erthylu."

#~ msgid "Integrity check failed"
#~ msgstr "Methodd y prawf cywirdeb"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The integrity check for ${PACKAGE} failed. It is most likely corrupt. "
#~ "Aborting."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Methodd y prawd cywirdeb ar gyfer ${PACKAGE}. Mwy na thebyg, mae'n "
#~ "llygredig. Yn erthylu."

#~ msgid "No installer components found"
#~ msgstr "Ni chanfuwyd unrhyw gydran sefydlydd"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you are installing from CD, it may be corrupt. If you are installing "
#~ "from a network, please try another mirror. If you are installing from  "
#~ "floppy, make sure you have a driver floppy in the correct drive."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Os ydych chi'n sefydlu o CD, efallai ei fod e'n llygr. Os ydych chi'n "
#~ "sefydlu o rhwydwaith, ceisiwch ddrych arall os gwelwch yn dda. Os ydych "
#~ "chi'n sefydlu o ddisgen hyblyg, sicrhewch fod gennych ddisgen gyrrydion "
#~ "yn y gyrriant cywir."
